"help21" = "Those that have a negative value are considered \"unpleasant\".\n\n";
"help22" = "In the world of Level 2, you cannot avoid experiencing some unpleasant experiences.\n\n";
"help23" = "Just try to generate a sequence that includes as few unpleasant experiences as possible.\n\n";
